    <title>Arctic contributor: Ed Struzik</title>
    <description>Canadian author and photographer Ed Struzik has been writing on the Arctic for more than three decades. He was the 2007 recipient of the Atkinson Fellowship in Public Policy and was a finalist for the 2008 Grantham Prize for Excellence in Reporting on the Environment. Ed is currently a fellow in the School of Policy Studies, Institute for Energy and Environmental Policy at Queen’s University.
</description>
